snippet.title: Melting Moon DEMO - BISHONEN, FANTASY & HORROR, Manly Let's Play
snippet.description:
Melting Moon is a rpg maker horror game about a girl lost in another world with four very pretty men who speak in vague intentions. Damn, so pretty.

Game Info & Download: http://meltingmoon-project.tumblr.com/
Game Playlist: https://goo.gl/pUl1RY
